      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new horror anthology and i need some help with a setting idea. i want to write a story set in a part of a city that feels really heavy and dangerous—like a neighborhood where people are always looking over their shoulders. specifically, i want it to be a heavily Black urban area that's been neglected by the city. can u help me brainstorm some spooky or unsettling themes for a story set there?",
