      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's getting there. the atmosphere is definitely heavy. you mentioned the children being \"born and raised in this crucible of shadows\"—can you continue that? i want to see how that affects them specifically. do they act differently than kids in other neighborhoods? like, is there a certain way they behave or a different kind of \"energy\" they have because of the environment? maybe lean into that idea of them being more attuned to the darker or more primal side of the neighborhood.",
